<item>
            <title>[LU-5478] Get rid of typedefs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5478</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Per request from upstream kernel maintainer we need to remove use of most (all) typedefs in Lustre kernel code.&lt;br/&gt;
Many of them are indeed have little sense and only add confusion.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This ticket is to track those patches.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
